      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or a source for parts. The engine requires significant work to be roadworthy, and the body shows extensive wear, including deep scratches, rust spots, and faded paint. The interior is also heavily worn with tears in the upholstery and non-functioning electronics. It is priced to reflect these substantial needs and is sold strictly as-is.",
