      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all project lovers and DIY enthusiasts! This car is ready for a transformation and represents a fantastic opportunity for someone who enjoys getting their hands dirty. While it's currently in poor condition and needs both mechanical and cosmetic attention, it\u2019s the perfect blank canvas to build your dream ride from the ground up!",
